metadata.description: Built on the foundation that food brings people together, Superordinary Friends is a collection of 2500 unique avatars each holding iconic food items. You’ll always find your Superordinary Friends with something in their hands. These limited edition illustrations combine quirky visual appeal with nuanced storytelling – showcasing the bonds of friendship, and our society’s love for bonding over good food.
metadata.name: Superordinary Friends #1
